ai-patthana16.67:0.2_0: Having given the immaculateness of the Dhamma
ai-patthana16.67:0.3_0: Seeing for what is called rejection of requisites,
ai-patthana16.67:1.1_0: Not seeing the Dhamma that arises in someone whose mind is not conditioned by not grasping, conditioned by conditions,
ai-patthana16.67:1.1_1: Such is the cause, condition for the don’t give rise to repulsion. ...
ai-patthana16.67:1.1_2: Such things don’t arise, or if they don’t give rise to the higher mind.
ai-patthana16.67:1.1_3: This is the section in brief.
